</p>
<!--template match = paragraph--><p>
Alternate or sometimes opposite near the apex of the twigs, unifoliolate, entirely glabrous; petiole 0.4-3(-5) cm long, canaliculate above, slightly bipulvinate, articulate at apex; lamina elliptic to slightly oblanceolate, 5.5-18.5 × 
1.7-7.4 cm
