1-3.5 mm
from leaf margin; tertiary and quaternary veins concolorous and prominent on lower leaf surface, the former parallel to the secondaries, the latter reticulate forming areolae 
c.
1 mm
wide; glandular dots dense and rather conspicuous on lower leaf surface,2-5 per mm².
</p>
<!--template match = paragraph--><p>
